    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but even if i distract myself, it doesn't change the fact that there's no actual goal at the end of all this. if life is just an endless cycle of pain and nothing actually matters in the long run, doesn't that make the choice to just stop... i dont know, logically valid? like, if the value of living and the value of not living are both zero, why is one better than the other?",
